                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-236-off1327 t18321129-236-crimeloc1329"></join>; the prisoner lodged a fortnight with me. I had a large clothes-chest there, which was broken open, and a set of bed-furniture, a counterpane, and the other articles stated, taken from it; I was informed he had gone out, and took him in a public-house, offering the counterpane for sale.</p>
